verse.lines:
{lang-eng}To God be the glory, great things He has done;
So loved He the world that He gave us His Son,
Who yielded His life an atonement for sin
And opened the life-gates that all may come in.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}O perfect redemption, the purchase of blood,
To ev’ry believer the promise of God;
The vilest offender who truly believes,
That moment from Jesus a pardon receives.{/lang-eng}
